Package: diagnoser
Type: Package
Title: Diagnostic tools for regression modeling
Version: 0.0.2.5
Author: Robert Schnitman <robertschnitman@gmail.com>
Maintainer: Robert Schnitman <robertschnitman@gmail.com>
Description: Plot residuals, store model results in a data frame, and compute common fit statistics.  The diagnose() family provides alternative graphs to Base R's plot(model.object). Additional functions--inspired by the broom library--calculate margin of errors and confidence intervals alongside regression results.
URL: https://github.com/robertschnitman/diagnoser
BugReports: https://github.com/robertschnitman/diagnoser/issues
Depends: R (>= 3.4.2), lazyeval (>= 0.2.1)
Imports: ggplot2 (>= 2.2.1), gridExtra (>= 2.3), scales (>= 0.5.0), car (>= 2.1)
License: GNU General Public License v3.0
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: TRUE
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
Date/Publication: 2017-11-14
